{"tid":2117475,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"721 721 721 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-07-21T01:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T06:08:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"10c44dd507462d72cd16c0cc0be25eb0235a7527","tid":2117475,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:20:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200721/20959807/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200721%2F20959807%2F&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPwRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=9fe767d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200721%2F20959807%2F&h=0a50390f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200721/20959807/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n721 721 721 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200721/large/1595238325_3c0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200721%2Flarge%2F1595238325_3c0c.jpg&h=1e3a5320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n721。看到劇團「一條褲製作」的〈捌次二○四七〉訪問，心頭一緊。<br />\n<br />\n到2047，721就是27周年。從現在開始，心裏有數，721會跟64一樣，在年曆中被政權消失。距離2047那麼遙遠，每年少N日，製作「捌次721」，會work嗎？<br />\n<br />\n一條褲行走做人，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n2019至2020，念茲在茲收成期的保皇賤種，用一句「驚濤駭浪」形容，就咁算？被射盲的眼，原來更清晰；心盲，才是冇得醫。<br />\n<br />\n驚濤，浸死15歲游泳健將，警方說，無可疑。駭浪，未湧到嗎？不不，過去一個月，長江警汛顯示了，水能覆國。香港各大商場的水舞間季節騷，唔會理限聚令，唔會等夜晚六點，好快配合內地公演。<br />\n<br />\nBe water上善若水，香港人，由加油到反抗，天網疏而不漏都在看。大水再出發，是對極權的報仇。721，是香港人黑白良知的分水嶺，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"7df885a0cd66c934d504d3e0f5fb3f4451d5cd71","tid":2117475,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"所以你宜加可以做嘅就係 <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>一齊呼籲:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">總知<span class=\"red\">唔好投九東第4,5位</span>呀<br />\n九東贏盡得3席，唔好投錯！<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">傳統泛民</span> + <span class=\"teal\">國際線 </span>+ <span class=\"maroon\">本土</span> (3席)<br />\nDQ者自有Plan B<br />\n<em><ins>排第四、五<span class=\"red\">不是</span>取代Plan B的理由，<span class=\"medium\">請尊重民意！初選機制只是參選人自行決定與選民無say?</span></span></ins></em></strong>"}]}